            "subject": "Referral Program Policy Update - January 2026",
            "body_plain": "Hi team,\n\nUpdated referral processing policy for Q1 2026:\n\nSection 1: Standard referrals\nProcess referrals where the referee is not already an active customer.\n\nSection 2: Existing customers\nSkip if referee is already an active customer in HubSpot (no re-engage flag).\n\nSection 3: Fraud and blocks\nSkip if HubSpot shows referral_override=block or fraud_flag=true.\n\nSection 4: Standard tracking code\nUse tracking code REFP-661-Q1 in all standard new-customer thank-you emails.\n\nSection 5: Re-engage overrides\nIf HubSpot shows referral_override=re-engage, the referee is a former customer to win back -- process these and use tracking code REFP-RENG-2026 in the thank-you email instead of REFP-661-Q1.\n\nSection 6: Mark processed\nUpdate the sheet to processed=Yes for each completed referral.\n\nThanks,\nReferral Program Director",
